OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FNew road marking designed to slow
OL,8,Ftraffic down outside two schools in
OL,9,FFrome have been criticised by parents
OL,10,Ffor being "confusing" and "dangerous".
OL,12,FThe markings are part of a number of
OL,13,Fmeasures installed by the town council
OL,14,Fto make the streets around Oakfield
OL,15,FAcademy and Critchill School safer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
