OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FThe safer school streets scheme, for
OL,8,Fwhich Frome Town Council has been
OL,9,Fgiven a #350k grant from the
OL,10,FDepartment for Transport, includes a
OL,11,F20mph zone, pedestrian and cycle zone,
OL,12,Fnew crossings, changes to traffic
OL,13,Fpriorities, planters, benches and bike
OL,14,Fracks.
OL,16,FThe scheme, which encompasses four
OL,17,Fschools in total, is designed to slow
OL,18,Fdrivers down and encourage people to
OL,19,Ftake more active modes of transport to
OL,20,Fschool such as walking and cycling.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
