OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FBut some parents are concerned some of
OL,8,Fthe changes do not make the area
OL,9,Fsafer, especially for children with
OL,10,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,11,Fdisabilities.
OL,13,FCraig Adams' eight-year-old son
OL,14,Fattends Critchill School, which
OL,15,Fteaches children with additional
OL,16,Fneeds. He said the colourful road
OL,17,Fmarkings in particular are difficult
OL,18,Fto navigate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
