OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1728077022
OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FHe said: "They're round dots, they
OL,8,Fmirror a lot of the things in the
OL,9,Fplayground.
OL,11,F"My son has autism, additional needs,
OL,12,Fso to try and explain to him that it's
OL,13,Fsafe to play in the playground, but
OL,14,Fthe same colours, the same shapes and
OL,15,Fthings on the road are not a safe
OL,16,Fspace to play. That can be very
OL,17,Fdifficult for him to understand."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
