OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FCraig said he thinks the money spent
OL,8,Fon the scheme would have been better
OL,9,Fused in other areas, such as foodbanks
OL,10,Fand support for families struggling
OL,11,Fwith the cost of living.
OL,13,FKaren O'Connell, whose daughters go to
OL,14,Fschool in Frome, said she was
OL,15,Fconcerned the new traffic priorities
OL,16,Fwere making it easier for drivers to
OL,17,Fspeed and there was confusion over the
OL,18,Fuse of informal crossings, which left
OL,19,Fdrivers and pedestrians unsure who had
OL,20,Fright-of-way.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
