OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FKaren said: "I think it's very
OL,8,Fdangerous. I feel like it's an
OL,9,Faccident waiting to happen, none of
OL,10,Fthese road markings are in the highway
OL,11,Fcode.
OL,13,F"Personally, I feel that the coloured
OL,14,Fmarkings in the roads are confusing
OL,15,Ffor children, especially special needs
OL,16,Fchildren and first school children.
OL,18,F"It's like a playground. They feel
OL,19,Fthat they can jump in the spots, my
OL,20,Fdaughter thought it looked like
OL,21,FTwister in the road."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
