OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FFrome Town Council said the safer
OL,8,Fschool street scheme money was awarded
OL,9,Fto them by the Department for
OL,10,FTransport, and following a
OL,11,Fconsultation, asked a transport
OL,12,Fcharity called Sustrans to design and
OL,13,Fcarry out the work.
OL,15,FThe council also said the traffic
OL,16,Fcalming measures were in place on a
OL,17,Ftrial basis and residents and parents
OL,18,Fconcerns would be listened to.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
