OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,FCllr Anita Collier, from Frome Town
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "We want desperately to
OL,9,Fhave that feedback. These things can
OL,10,Fbe changed.
OL,12,F"Sustrans have actually made changes
OL,13,Fto their designs throughout the
OL,14,Fcountry. We know that that's possible.
OL,16,F"It will come as a cost. But this
OL,17,Fwhole scheme has been funded by
OL,18,Fgovernment money that comes from the
OL,19,FDepartment of Transport.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
