OL,3,CNew road marking to slow traffic
OL,4,Coutside schools 'confusing' and
OL,5,C'dangerous'
OL,7,F"We know there are trials and that
OL,8,Fwill be built in (to the cost),
OL,9,Fchanges may have to be made."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Sustrans said:
OL,12,F"Colourful street markings are a
OL,13,Fcommon proposal in school street
OL,14,Fdesigns.
OL,16,F"They alert drivers to the fact that
OL,17,Fthere may be people around the street
OL,18,Fand, as part of a larger package of
OL,19,Ftraffic calming measures, encourage
OL,20,Fthem to slow down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
