OL,7,F"The street markings around Frome
OL,8,Fsafer school streets were created
OL,9,Fthrough a collaborative co-design
OL,10,Fprocess with the community including
OL,11,Fpupils from the local schools.
OL,12,FResidents from the local streets
OL,13,Fhelped to choose the designs."
OL,15,FThe company added that a Road Safety
OL,16,FAudit (RSA) was carried out on the
OL,17,Fdesigns before construction, and there
OL,18,Fis due to be another Safety Audit
OL,19,Ffollowing the completion of works.
